### Architectural Concerns (added to tech-debt.md)
1. `detect_version()` defaults to V1_3 — may misidentify future older configs without explicit version field
2. Clipboard code in `config_export.py` creates `tk.Tk()` root per operation — risks conflicts in GUI mode
